description:
FinanceXSTO is one of the project provided by Next Generation Exchange Ltd. (hereinafter FinanceX). We issue Security Token Offerings (STO) named FNXS based on FinanceX’s assets including Blockchain services and products with the key in our development strategy in 2018 - 2025 is FinanceX exchange.

FinanceX is a world-class digital asset that provides the ability to trade with any local currencies (Fiat) in a fast and convenient way in Southeast Asia and Asia Pacific countries.
name: FinanceX Exchange Token
